    "rich_text_Xj7QBY": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_CPwYAY": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "TABASQUISHY® VIP CLUB"
          }
        },
        "heading_EGxpCx": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "TABA Rewards, now better than ever",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h3",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_XfVjdX": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our upgraded loyalty program gives you more ways to earn, clearer ways to redeem, and even more exclusive perks to unlock as you grow with us.</p><p>You can now earn rewards through shopping, reviews, referrals, and VIP milestones — all while enjoying a simpler and more valuable rewards experience.</p><p>Because being part of the TABA community should feel rewarding from day one.</p><ul><li><h4><strong>Earn TABA Coins your way</strong></h4></li></ul><p>Collect TABA Coins through shopping, celebrating, sharing, and writing product reviews. Every interaction brings you closer to your next reward.</p><p><strong>Now including: Write a product review +100 TABA Coins</strong></p><ul><li><h4><strong>Redeeming your rewards is now easier than ever</strong></h4></li></ul><p>We’ve simplified our rewards so you can choose the option that works best for you.</p><p><strong>Choose how to redeem</strong></p><ul><li><strong>100 TABA Coins = $1 off</strong></li><li><strong>1000 TABA Coins = 15% off coupon</strong></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><h4><strong>Share the love, get rewarded</strong></h4></li></ul><p>Invite your friends to discover TABASQUISHY and enjoy rewards together.</p><p><strong>Give 15% off, get 15% off</strong><br/>When your friend shops with your referral link, they’ll get <strong>15% off</strong> — and you’ll get <strong>15% off too</strong>.</p><ul><li><h4><strong>Unlock more as you level up</strong></h4></li></ul><p>Our VIP program is designed to reward your loyalty with bonus rewards, early access, exclusive previews, and members-only perks.</p><p>The more you grow with us, the more you unlock.</p><p><strong>Bronze</strong><br/><br/>A rewarding start with bonus Coins, early access, and members-only restock alerts.</p><p><strong>Entry reward</strong></p><ul><li>20 TABA Coins</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>Early access to selected launches</li><li>Members-only restock alerts</li></ul><p><strong>Silver</strong><br/><br/>Unlock bigger rewards, a gift card, a 15% off coupon, and even earlier access to what’s next.</p><p><strong>Entry rewards</strong></p><ul><li>200 TABA Coins</li><li>$5 gift card</li><li>15% off coupon</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>24-hour early access to new drops</li><li>Priority customer support</li><li>Exclusive VIP-only previews</li></ul><p><strong>Gold</strong><br/><br/>Bigger rewards, deeper access, and exclusive surprises for our most loyal members.</p><p><strong>Entry rewards</strong></p><ul><li>500 TABA Coins</li><li>18% off coupon</li><li>Two $10 gift cards</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>Earliest access to limited editions</li><li>VIP-exclusive surprise offers</li><li>Priority restock access</li><li>Birthday month special gift access</li></ul>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        },
        "heading_JFrdV6": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Earn TABA Coins your way",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h3",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_yr8mBt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Collect TABA Coins through shopping, celebrating, sharing, and writing product reviews. Every interaction brings you closer to your next reward.</p><p><strong>Now including: Write a product review +100 TABA Coins</strong></p>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        },
        "heading_nf36Vm": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Redeeming your rewards is now easier than ever",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h3",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_JB7W88": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We’ve simplified our rewards so you can choose the option that works best for you.</p><p><strong>Choose how to redeem</strong></p><ul><li><strong>100 TABA Coins = $1 off</strong></li><li><strong>1000 TABA Coins = 15% off coupon</strong></li></ul>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        },
        "heading_zrmHyw": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Share the love, get rewarded",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h3",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_FNUd4i": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Invite your friends to discover TABASQUISHY and enjoy rewards together.</p><p><strong>Give 15% off, get 15% off</strong><br/>When your friend shops with your referral link, they’ll get <strong>15% off</strong> — and you’ll get <strong>15% off too</strong>.</p>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        },
        "heading_QKeiqR": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Unlock more as you level up",
            "marker_style": "style1",
            "size": "h3",
            "marker_color": "#fd6262"
          }
        },
        "text_hV88Ty": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our VIP program is designed to reward your loyalty with bonus rewards, early access, exclusive previews, and members-only perks.</p><p>The more you grow with us, the more you unlock.</p><p><strong>👑 Bronze</strong><br/><br/>A rewarding start with bonus Coins, early access, and members-only restock alerts.</p><p><strong>Entry reward</strong></p><ul><li>20 TABA Coins</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>Early access to selected launches</li><li>Members-only restock alerts</li></ul><p><strong>👑 Silver</strong><br/><br/>Unlock bigger rewards, a gift card, a 15% off coupon, and even earlier access to what’s next.</p><p><strong>Entry rewards</strong></p><ul><li>200 TABA Coins</li><li>$5 gift card</li><li>15% off coupon</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>24-hour early access to new drops</li><li>Priority customer support</li><li>Exclusive VIP-only previews</li></ul><p><strong>👑 Gold</strong><br/><br/>Bigger rewards, deeper access, and exclusive surprises for our most loyal members.</p><p><strong>Entry rewards</strong></p><ul><li>500 TABA Coins</li><li>18% off coupon</li><li>Two $10 gift cards</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>Earliest access to limited editions</li><li>VIP-exclusive surprise offers</li><li>Priority restock access</li><li>Birthday month special gift access</li></ul>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        },
        "subheading_t3WApP": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Can guest customers earn TABA Coins?"
          }
        },
        "subheading_XYntTt": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Yes. Even if you check out as a guest, you can still earn TABA Coins and participate in parts of our loyalty program.Here’s how it works:Your loyalty activity is recorded based on the email address used at checkout.If you later create an account using the same email address, your eligible TABA Coins and loyalty activity can be recognized and made available in your account.If you sign up with a different email address, the system may not recognize those past guest orders as belonging to the same customer, so your previous points or loyalty activity may not appear automatically.Please note that you’ll need to create or activate an account in order to access, redeem, and use your rewards."
          }
        }
      },
