    "collapsible_content_XQ4hf8": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_XFLQBy": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the TABA Loyalty Program?",
            "open": true,
            "content": "<p>The TABA Loyalty Program is our way of rewarding you for shopping, engaging, and growing with us.</p><p><br/></p><p>You can earn <strong>TABA Coins</strong> through eligible actions like placing orders, signing up, celebrating your birthday, following us, sharing with friends, and writing product reviews. You can then redeem your Coins for rewards and unlock even more perks through our VIP tiers.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_AxhG73": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I earn TABA Coins?",
            "open": true,
            "content": "<p>You can currently earn TABA Coins through the following actions:</p><ul><li><strong>Place an order</strong> — earn <strong>6 TABA Coins for every $1 spent</strong></li><li><strong>Sign up</strong> — earn <strong>150 TABA Coins</strong></li><li><strong>Celebrate a birthday</strong> — earn <strong>100 TABA Coins</strong></li><li><strong>Share on Facebook</strong> — earn <strong>50 TABA Coins</strong></li><li><strong>Follow on Instagram</strong> — earn <strong>25 TABA Coins</strong></li><li><strong>Write a product review</strong> — earn <strong>100 TABA Coins</strong></li></ul><p>Eligible actions may be updated from time to time as our loyalty program evolves.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_xtmLdn": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I redeem my TABA Coins?",
            "open": true,
            "content": "<p>You can currently redeem your TABA Coins in two ways:</p><ul><li><strong>100 TABA Coins = $1 off</strong></li><li><strong>1000 TABA Coins = 15% off coupon</strong></li></ul><p>To redeem:</p><ol><li>Log in to your account</li><li>Open the <strong>Rewards panel</strong></li><li>Choose the reward you want</li><li>Redeem your TABA Coins</li><li>Apply the reward code at checkout</li></ol>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_mhn67b": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are TABA Coins applied automatically at checkout?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>No. TABA Coins are <strong>not automatically deducted at checkout</strong>.</p><p>You’ll need to redeem your Coins in the <strong>Rewards panel</strong> first. Once redeemed, you’ll receive a reward or discount code that can be applied during checkout.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_XY94yK": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use my TABA Coins directly like cash?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Not directly at checkout.</p><p>TABA Coins need to be <strong>converted into a reward first</strong> through the Rewards panel. Once you redeem them, you can use the reward code on your order.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_eiayfj": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I check my TABA Coins balance?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>You can check your balance by opening the <strong>TABA Coin</strong> entry at the bottom right corner of the page. Once inside, you’ll be able to see your <strong>TABA Coins balance</strong>, <strong>available rewards</strong>, and <strong>VIP status</strong>.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_Mzrzqp": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do TABA Coins expire?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes.</p><p>Customer points begin to expire after <strong>365 days</strong>. We recommend checking your balance regularly and redeeming your TABA Coins before they expire.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_VqxzxV": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use multiple rewards at the same time?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>This may depend on how discounts are applied at checkout and whether other promotions are active. In general, some rewards may not be combinable with other discounts or offers.</p><p>If you’re unsure whether a reward can be used with another promotion, please contact us before placing your order.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_wbWRLN": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the referral program?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Our referral program lets you share TABASQUISHY with friends and get rewarded when they shop.</p><h3><strong>Current referral offer:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Your friend gets 15% off</strong></li><li><strong>You get 15% off too</strong></li></ul><p>It’s our way of saying thanks for spreading the squishy love.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_UmRxbn": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does the referral reward work?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>When you share your referral link with a friend and they make a qualifying purchase, they’ll receive <strong>15% off</strong>, and you’ll receive your <strong>15% off reward</strong> too.</p><p>Make sure your friend uses your referral link correctly so the referral can be tracked.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_E39Ley": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are VIP tiers?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Our VIP program rewards you as you continue shopping with us. The more TABA Coins you earn, the more exclusive rewards and perks you unlock.</p><h3><strong>VIP tiers:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Bronze</strong> — starts at <strong>0 TABA Coins</strong></li><li><strong>Silver</strong> — unlocks at <strong>1,000 TABA Coins</strong></li><li><strong>Gold</strong> — unlocks at <strong>2,500 TABA Coins</strong></li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_hcdtjr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What do I get when I enter a VIP tier?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Each VIP tier includes <strong>entry rewards</strong> and <strong>tier perks</strong>.</p><h3><strong>Bronze</strong></h3><p><strong>Entry reward</strong></p><ul><li>20 TABA Coins</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>Early access to selected launches</li><li>Members-only restock alerts</li></ul><h3><strong>Silver</strong></h3><p><strong>Entry rewards</strong></p><ul><li>200 TABA Coins</li><li>$5 gift card</li><li>15% off coupon</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>24-hour early access to new drops</li><li>Priority customer support</li><li>Exclusive VIP-only previews</li></ul><h3><strong>Gold</strong></h3><p><strong>Entry rewards</strong></p><ul><li>500 TABA Coins</li><li>18% off coupon</li><li>Two $10 gift cards</li></ul><p><strong>Perks</strong></p><ul><li>Earliest access to limited editions</li><li>VIP-exclusive surprise offers</li><li>Priority restock access</li><li>Birthday month special gift access</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_TFUVhb": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the difference between entry rewards and tier perks?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Entry rewards</strong> are one-time rewards you receive when you enter a new VIP tier.</p><p><strong>Tier perks</strong> are the ongoing benefits that come with being in that tier.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_CtBbpK": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do I get VIP rewards every time I place an order?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Not exactly.</p><p>Your regular orders can help you earn TABA Coins, and earning more Coins can help you move up VIP tiers.<br/><br/>However, <strong>entry rewards</strong> are only awarded <strong>once when you enter a tier</strong>, not every time you place an order.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_y4EMDB": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I earn TABA Coins from writing a review?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes.<br/><br/>You can earn <strong>100 TABA Coins</strong> for writing a product review.</p><p>This is a great way to earn extra Coins while helping other customers discover products they’ll love.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_3Krpny": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I transfer my TABA Coins to someone else?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>TABA Coins are tied to your account and are generally not transferable.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_KxKat7": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What happens if I return or cancel an order?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>If an order is canceled or refunded, any TABA Coins associated with that order may be adjusted accordingly.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_mFyRPh": {
